author: Divya Rao
title: Photo: Amitabh Bachchan’s Granddaughter Navya Nanda Is Quite The Stunner
text:
Divya Rao Feb . 23 . 2017 
Amitabh Bachchan ‘s granddaughter Navya Naveli Nanda is one of the most popular star kids on social media. She already has a massive fan following and people can’t help but wonder if she’ll take after her grandparents and venture into the world of Bollywood. Only time will tell. Navya shared this lovely photo of her with her ‘new’ friend in New York and she looks stunning! Take a look. A post shared by Navya Naveli Nanda (@navya__nanda) on Feb 22, 2017 at 1:18am PST 
Tall and gorgeous!
